flowchart LR
    U[User / App] --> AG[HindsightMemoryAgent]
    AG --> SS[SQLiteStore]
    AG --> VEC[SQLiteVecAdapter]
    AG --> FK[FalkorDB Lite]
    SS --> DB[SQLite DB]
    VEC --> IDX[sqlite-vec extension or fallback table]
    IDX --> DB

    subgraph SQLite
      SS --> DB
    end

    subgraph VectorIndex
      VEC --> IDX
      IDX --> DB
    end

    subgraph GraphProjection
      AG --> FK
    end

    AG -->|ingest_text/add_edge| SS
    AG -->|recall query| SS
    AG -->|optional vector recall| VEC
    AG -->|project graph edges| FK
    SS -->|persist documents and edges| DB
    FK -->|local KB queries| AG
